Notes

Time is displayed in ms.

Median of a sorted sequence is calculated using the formula:
- if n is odd - Median (M) = value of ((n + 1)/2)th item term
- if n is even - Median (M) = value of [((n)/2)th item term + ((n)/2 + 1)th item term]/2

Variation is calculated using the formula - 100 * (MAX_TIME - MIN_TIME) / MAX_TIME

Deviation is calculated using the formula - last_jobID_execution_time / avg_time_of_jobIds
